**What do you intend to achieve by the set date and how?
Our set date would be around before the 6th of September 2021 where in this date we would be able to achieve:
  - Completing the mechanics for the Giant and Fairy character
  - Establish a menu system, as well as, the scoring system, loading and saving game state.
  - Have a finished tutorial and first level
  - Create the design and animation for the Giant and Fairy character

**Who is handling what task?
- Caitlin (thomascait) is responsible for the Fairy character's mechanics which would be the Fairy's gliding movement, particle effects and lighting a torch interaction.
- Jeff (wanghaow) is our designer and is responsible for creating the character models of the Giant and Fairy, as well as, designing and animating their movements. 
- Katrina (kellykatr) is responsible for creating the first level level map and design and also helping with the Fairy character's mechanics.
- Laurence (malatalaur) is handling half of the Giant character's mechanics which would be pushing objects and the pressure plate mechanic, which would also involved multiple interactable objects.
- Nathaniel (raisnat) is handling the other half of the Giant character's mechanics which would be breaking object and create with the tutorial level design and map.
- Patrick (laingpatr) will be handling the menu and scoring system, as well as, the loading and saving game states.

**When will these tasks be completed by/.
***1st Week (Monday 9th - Friday 13th August)
  - Monday 9th of August, Nathan aims to complete the Giant's breaking object interaction.
  - Wednesday 11th of August, Laurence aims to complete the Giant's pushing object interaction.
  - Friday 13th of August, Katrina aims to complete the first level design.
  - Saturday, Jeff aims to complete the mouldering of the characters (Giant and Fairy).
***2nd Week (Monday 16th - Friday 21st August)
  - Monday, Laurence aims to create interactions with the pressure plate mechanic.
  - Tuesday, Nathan aims to readjust blueprint for the Giant character.
  - Wednesday, Patrick aims to sort out the menu system of the game.
  - Friday, Jeff aims to complete the rigging of the characters (Giant and Fairy).
***3rd Week (Monday 23rd - Friday 27th August)
  - Monday 23rd of August, Patrick aims to complete the menu and scoring system.
  - Wednesday, Patrick aims to sort out the User Interface of the game.
  - Thursday, Laurence aims to complete the designs for buttons and overlays for UI widgets.
  - Friday, Jeff aims to create 3D animal assets (bird, tiger, bear, etc).
***4th Week (Monday 30th August - Friday 3rd September)
  - Monday, Jeff plans to create environmental 3D assets (rocks, landscape, trees, etc).
